'''Herbert Boucher Dobbie''' (13 February 1852&ndash;8 August 1940) was a New Zealand engineering draughtsman, botanist, stationmaster, orchardist and writer. He was born in [[Hayes, Hillingdon|Hayes]], [[Middlesex]], [[England]], on 13 February 1852.<ref name="DNZB Dobbie">{{DNZB|title=Herbert Boucher Dobbie|first= John D.|last= McCraw|id=3d9|accessdate=23 April 2017}}</ref>

